I found a way to hear that.

24:05.717 --> 24:07.803
I found a way to believe that.

24:08.672 --> 24:10.295
And I...

24:11.958 --> 24:13.796
I found a way to move forward.

24:14.160 --> 24:15.843
You got therapy.

24:17.306 --> 24:18.389
Yeah.

24:18.491 --> 24:20.232
You moved forward.

24:22.335 --> 24:24.002
Mm-hmm.

24:25.138 --> 24:27.606
And you didn't once try and find me?

24:31.373 --> 24:33.616
I was petrified.

24:36.318 --> 24:40.403
I was petrified every single
moment of my pregnancy.

24:40.653 --> 24:43.538
I mean, it was bad enough that
I had to see his face

24:43.623 --> 24:45.407
every day in class.

24:45.545 --> 24:47.548
I was so terrified...

24:48.452 --> 24:52.996
imagining that
you'd be a boy

24:53.832 --> 24:57.757
and that you'd have his face
and his voice.

24:57.866 --> 25:01.723
And every day,
every kick, every movement,

25:01.808 --> 25:04.558
it just reminded me
where you came from.

25:07.046 --> 25:10.765
But, you know, movies and books
and... and magazines,

25:10.850 --> 25:13.538
they just kept talking about this...

25:14.927 --> 25:19.747
love that you feel
the minute your baby is born.

25:20.059 --> 25:21.609
How instantaneous it is

25:21.694 --> 25:24.991
and how, um, your heart
just cracks wide open, and...

25:25.170 --> 25:26.487
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

25:26.765 --> 25:29.163
And I remember,
I kept telling myself

25:29.702 --> 25:31.644
that as soon as
I had you in my arms

25:31.730 --> 25:33.413
that I could do that

25:34.102 --> 25:35.687
and that I would do that.

25:36.042 --> 25:40.484
Other women did it,
so why couldn't I?

25:41.007 --> 25:43.866
So I gave the hospital
a fake name.

25:43.952 --> 25:48.359
I left with you...
the day you were born.

25:48.480 --> 25:49.944
I remember they wanted me to stay,

25:50.030 --> 25:51.836
and they wanted me to rest,
but I just wanted to get out.

25:51.921 --> 25:54.273
I just wanted to get out of
there, and I just wanted...

25:58.164 --> 25:59.953
<font color="#ff8080">[Voice breaking]</font> I just
wanted to be alone with you,

26:00.038 --> 26:02.417
and I just wanted it to be
the two of us, and...

26:02.502 --> 26:04.710
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes deeply]</font>

26:04.930 --> 26:07.593
...and I wanted to stare
at you and hold you...

26:11.310 --> 26:13.244
...'til that love came.

26:15.155 --> 26:16.773
But it never did.

26:17.484 --> 26:19.116
No, it did.

26:21.109 --> 26:22.103
It did.

26:22.188 --> 26:24.805
Everything they said
was absolutely right.

26:26.025 --> 26:28.507
My heart cracked wide open.

26:29.593 --> 26:31.163
<font color="#ff8080">[Crying]</font>

26:32.966 --> 26:34.516
It was never just us,

26:34.601 --> 26:37.276
no matter how hard I tried,
no matter what I did.

26:38.242 --> 26:40.718
I was just a reminder of him.

26:41.435 --> 26:43.819
I resented you
so much for it.

26:47.213 --> 26:49.335
I spent most of my life...

26:50.454 --> 26:53.890
doubting everyone
I ever met,

26:55.088 --> 26:57.755
leaving them before
they could leave me.

26:58.870 --> 27:00.137
I am a grown woman.

27:00.276 --> 27:01.765
<font color="#ff8080">[Sighs]</font>

27:02.428 --> 27:05.856
With a job that I love
and friends I love

27:05.997 --> 27:07.926
and a husband
who loves me,

27:08.012 --> 27:09.642
and still...

27:10.517 --> 27:11.824
still...

27:13.343 --> 27:17.394
I was walking around, uh,
\waiting,

27:19.012 --> 27:21.114
wondering if you would ever
find me.

27:21.538 --> 27:22.844
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

27:23.074 --> 27:25.824
If you would ever say that
you're sorry.

27:29.422 --> 27:30.621
I did the best I could.

27:30.707 --> 27:33.246
The best you could would've been
to find an adoption agency

27:33.332 --> 27:35.610
and make sure I had a home
and someone to love me,

27:35.695 --> 27:37.840
not toss me away like garbage.

27:38.878 --> 27:41.988
It is so easy
to look at me now

27:42.074 --> 27:43.051
and think of all the ways

27:43.137 --> 27:46.973
that I could've been
kinder, better, or smarter,

27:47.367 --> 27:48.606
but...

27:50.895 --> 27:53.278
...I was not the person
I am today.

27:53.364 --> 27:54.981
I was not in my right mind.

27:55.067 --> 27:57.416
I wasn't in my mind
at all.

27:59.403 --> 28:05.012
That night that...
that he held me down, screaming.

28:06.283 --> 28:09.335
That night that he had
his hands around my throat

28:09.629 --> 28:11.481
until I stopped screaming,

28:11.567 --> 28:13.864
when I was hovering over
my own body

28:13.950 --> 28:16.250
while he was tearing away
at me,

28:16.388 --> 28:18.912
that night that he smiled

28:19.072 --> 28:23.285
and he forced me to say
that I liked it,

28:24.384 --> 28:26.660
when he laughed and...

28:28.613 --> 28:32.149
...promised that we could do it
any time that I wanted to...

28:34.520 --> 28:38.790
...that was the night
that I lost my right mind.

28:40.285 --> 28:42.777
He stole it from me,
and for nine months...

28:42.862 --> 28:45.542
for nine months,
I pretended I was fine.

28:45.908 --> 28:48.234
I pretended that
I wasn't a zombie,

28:48.367 --> 28:51.285
that I wasn't numb
or dead inside.

28:51.904 --> 28:54.089
And then, the day that
you were born,

28:54.175 --> 28:57.503
I held you, and
I looked at your face,

28:57.589 --> 28:58.693
and I...

28:58.778 --> 29:01.195
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes deeply]</font>

29:01.472 --> 29:03.598
...I could feel again for the first time,

29:03.683 --> 29:05.120
but...

29:08.324 --> 29:09.707
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes sharply]</font>

29:09.855 --> 29:11.425
...my mind...

29:13.226 --> 29:14.902
...that took years to come back.

29:14.988 --> 29:17.729
In fact, I'm...
Part of it never did.

29:20.767 --> 29:23.003
Of course you deserved better.

29:26.639 --> 29:27.793
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes sharply]</font>

29:27.879 --> 29:30.167
I didn't have better to give you.

29:39.105 --> 29:40.668
I was seven weeks pregnant

29:40.753 --> 29:43.144
when my ex-husband cracked
my ribs

29:43.230 --> 29:45.550
and threw me across
the living room floor.

29:47.226 --> 29:48.855
He didn't know that I was pregnant,

29:48.941 --> 29:52.980
and I decided in that moment
that he could never know.

29:55.172 --> 29:58.175
I couldn't... I couldn't see a way out.

29:58.954 --> 30:00.420
Not then, at least.

30:00.506 --> 30:02.160
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathing shakily]</font>

30:02.338 --> 30:03.949
I knew that, if I tried to leave,

30:04.066 --> 30:05.574
he would kill me.

30:05.660 --> 30:08.730
But I also knew that
I couldn't raise a kid

30:08.815 --> 30:12.517
in that... fear, and in that danger.

30:14.032 --> 30:15.605
You had an abortion.

30:16.455 --> 30:18.144
I've never told anyone that.

30:19.759 --> 30:21.863
I don't know why.
I'm not ashamed of it.

30:21.949 --> 30:22.995
I...

30:23.081 --> 30:24.746
<font color="#ff8080">[Sighs]</font>

30:24.831 --> 30:27.120
I did what I had to do.

30:27.407 --> 30:28.824
<font color="#ff8080">[Crying]</font>

30:29.035 --> 30:31.686
<font color="#ff8080">[Vehicles passing in distance]</font>

30:31.771 --> 30:33.287
<font color="#ff8080">[Dinnerware clattering lightly
in distance]</font>

30:33.372 --> 30:34.855
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

30:40.646 --> 30:42.449
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

30:42.682 --> 30:44.282
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

30:47.019 --> 30:48.761
Do I look like him?

30:54.913 --> 30:57.074
You have my father's eyes...

30:59.036 --> 31:00.605
but the hair is all mine.

31:03.386 --> 31:05.878
And maybe the fire
in the belly.

31:09.141 --> 31:11.425
<font color="#ff8080">[Voice breaking]</font> I did the best I could,

31:11.608 --> 31:13.058
and I'm still...

31:16.238 --> 31:19.027
I'm sorry. I'm still
just doing the best I can.

31:24.724 --> 31:26.808
<font color="#ff8080">[Chair scrapes lightly]</font>

31:26.893 --> 31:28.643
<font color="#ff8080">[Exhales sharply]</font>

31:28.736 --> 31:32.628
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

31:32.988 --> 31:36.628
<font color="#fffff00">[♪♪]</font>

31:37.570 --> 31:39.153
<font color="#ff8080">[Footsteps depart]</font>

31:39.238 --> 31:43.535
<font color="#fffff00">[♪♪]</font>

31:44.813 --> 31:46.074
<font color="#ff8080">[Door closes]</font>

31:48.973 --> 31:51.411
She's becoming increasingly
tachypneic.

31:51.647 --> 31:53.721
Let OR 1 know that
we're on our way.

31:53.865 --> 31:55.723
Abby, it's time.

31:55.808 --> 31:57.005
We have to go up now.

31:57.091 --> 31:58.264
No. I'm not...
I'm not ready. I'm...

31:58.349 --> 32:00.061
<font color="#ff8080">[Echoing]</font> Abby, I know you're scared.

32:00.146 --> 32:01.366
No, you're gonna... you're gonna...

32:01.451 --> 32:04.298
you're gonna take me out
and knock me out where I...

32:04.383 --> 32:06.651
the last time I was out,
h-he knocked me out.

32:06.736 --> 32:07.935
<font color="#ff8080">[Echoing]</font> Abby. Abby, listen to me.

32:08.020 --> 32:10.427
If we don't do this surgery now,
it could kill you.

32:10.513 --> 32:12.263
<font color="#ff8080">[Crying]</font> I can't.

32:12.535 --> 32:15.419
I can't leave here, this room.

32:15.661 --> 32:17.979
Everyone has his face,
every man.

32:18.064 --> 32:19.614
It's all I see.

32:19.699 --> 32:21.749
Even when I
close my eyes...

32:21.834 --> 32:24.013
<font color="#ff8080">[Echoing]</font> Please.
I can't see his face.

32:24.099 --> 32:25.653
Please don't I...
make me see his face, please.

32:25.738 --> 32:27.575
<font color="#ff8080">[Normal voice]</font> You don't have to, Abby.

32:27.660 --> 32:29.116
- <font color="#ff8080">[Heartbeat pulsing]</font>
- You don't have to.

32:29.201 --> 32:31.248
<font color="#ff8080">[Whimpering]</font>

32:31.525 --> 32:32.634
Okay.

32:32.938 --> 32:36.677
Tuck says they're talking.
What is that? Talking?

32:37.474 --> 32:38.633
I think they're dating.

32:38.718 --> 32:40.982
Mnh. Why do they do that?

32:41.153 --> 32:42.966
Why do they insist
on coming up with new words

32:43.052 --> 32:44.805
when the old words were
just fine?

32:44.890 --> 32:46.423
<font color="#ff8080">[Chuckles]</font>

32:46.681 --> 32:48.571
It's not funny.

32:48.861 --> 32:51.298
Well, you... you do sound
a little, you know,

32:51.384 --> 32:52.579
"Get off my lawn!"

32:52.665 --> 32:53.681
No.

32:53.766 --> 32:56.345
I want him to be happy.

32:56.431 --> 32:57.923
I want him to, you know,

32:58.009 --> 33:00.486
have the butterflies
and first love and all that.

33:00.572 --> 33:02.079
Mm-hmm.
Yeah, just not so soon.

33:02.275 --> 33:03.884
<font color="#ff8080">[Sighs]</font>

33:04.210 --> 33:06.345
We're gonna have
to sit his butt down

33:06.462 --> 33:08.813
and teach him about respect...

33:10.384 --> 33:13.100
..empathy, consent.

33:13.185 --> 33:14.661
Condoms... Oh, dear Lord.

33:14.747 --> 33:16.466
I have to talk to my son
about condoms.

33:16.552 --> 33:18.172
- 100%.
- <font color="#ff8080">[Sighs]</font>

33:18.282 --> 33:19.592
Or...

33:21.241 --> 33:23.078
I could sit down with him.

33:23.715 --> 33:25.368
It can be on you.

33:26.669 --> 33:30.890
But my dad gave me this talk,
and it worked.

33:31.969 --> 33:33.844
<font color="#ff8080">[Cellphone vibrates, chimes]</font>

33:33.997 --> 33:35.614
Mm, I gotta go.

33:35.700 --> 33:39.250
<font color="#ff8080">[Indistinct conversations]</font>

33:39.979 --> 33:41.177
Oh, I'm sorry, sir.

33:41.263 --> 33:42.673
You, uh...
You can't go through there.

33:42.758 --> 33:43.899
Well, why not?

33:44.130 --> 33:46.116
Because I've been asked
to see that you don't.

33:46.202 --> 33:47.245
Wha...

33:47.987 --> 33:49.070
<font color="#ff8080">[Door opens, closes]</font>

33:49.427 --> 33:50.908
Well, but she can go?

33:50.994 --> 33:52.140
Yes, sir.

33:53.626 --> 33:55.894
<font color="#ff8080">[Indistinct conversations]</font>

33:59.999 --> 34:02.489
Dr. Karev asked us
to all stand here?

34:02.575 --> 34:03.496
Do we know why?

34:03.582 --> 34:06.446
Just... that a patient needs us.

34:07.042 --> 34:08.553
She needs all of us.

34:09.726 --> 34:10.866
Okay.

34:10.967 --> 34:13.702
<font color="#ff8080">[Conversations continue]</font>

34:14.163 --> 34:16.283
<font color="#00ff00">Female Nurse:</font> <i>Okay, ladies,
we need you all to line up</i>

34:16.407 --> 34:17.985
<i>either on the right side or left.</i>

34:18.071 --> 34:20.664
Please keep
this middle aisle clear.

34:22.266 --> 34:23.835
Are you ready?

34:23.956 --> 34:26.123
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes deeply]</font>

34:30.295 --> 34:34.047
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Standin' on the platform ♪</font></i>

34:34.132 --> 34:36.632
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Watching you go ♪</font></i>

34:36.824 --> 34:38.306
<font color="#fffff00">[♪♪]</font>

34:38.393 --> 34:39.969
Yes.

34:40.599 --> 34:43.650
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ It's like no other pain ♪</font></i>

34:44.007 --> 34:46.914
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I've ever known ♪</font></i>

34:47.360 --> 34:50.223
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

34:50.549 --> 34:53.600
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ To love someone so much ♪</font></i>

34:53.819 --> 34:56.914
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ To have no control ♪</font></i>

34:57.493 --> 35:00.177
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

35:00.496 --> 35:03.881
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ You said,
"I wanna see the world" ♪</font></i>

35:04.029 --> 35:07.438
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ And I said, "Go" ♪</font></i>

35:07.681 --> 35:12.071
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

35:12.872 --> 35:19.133
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ But I think I'm lost
without you ♪</font></i>

35:19.412 --> 35:23.414
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

35:23.722 --> 35:28.809
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Strangers rushin' past,
just tryna get home ♪</font></i>

35:28.988 --> 35:33.071
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

35:33.426 --> 35:38.946
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ You were the only
safehaven that I've known ♪</font></i>

35:39.031 --> 35:43.351
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

35:43.436 --> 35:45.820
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Hits me at full speed ♪</font></i>

35:45.965 --> 35:49.657
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Feel like I can't breathe ♪</font></i>

35:49.742 --> 35:53.794
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ And nobody knows ♪</font></i>

35:53.887 --> 35:58.739
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I think I'm lost without you ♪</font></i>

35:58.988 --> 36:00.138
Ready?

36:00.286 --> 36:03.989
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ You ♪</font></i>

36:04.256 --> 36:07.341
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I just feel crushed... ♪</font></i>
- I'm staying right here.

36:07.426 --> 36:11.879
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ ..Without you ♪</font></i>

36:11.964 --> 36:14.473
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ 'Cause I've been strong for so long ♪</font></i>

36:14.559 --> 36:17.118
- <font color="#ff8080">[Respirator hissing]</font>
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ That I never thought ♪</font></i>

36:17.203 --> 36:23.824
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ How much I love you ♪</font></i>

36:23.909 --> 36:25.226
<font color="#00ff00">Teddy:</font> I've seen soldiers like this.

36:25.311 --> 36:27.911
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Standin' on the platform, ♪
Young women and young men,</font></i>

36:27.997 --> 36:29.231
brutalized,
with no.

36:29.317 --> 36:31.030
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Watching you go ♪</font></i>
- idea how to talk about it.

36:31.116 --> 36:32.387
<font color="#ff8080">[Monitor beeping]</font>

36:32.473 --> 36:35.308
What you did today with Abby,
that was not protocol...

36:35.394 --> 36:37.317
-<i><font color="#ffff00"> ♪ You said, "I wanna see the world" ♪</font></i>
- I know, I know, and I'm sorry.

36:37.402 --> 36:41.019
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ And I said ♪</font></i>
- I'm saying it should be.

36:41.158 --> 36:43.535
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

36:43.698 --> 36:45.128
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ "Go" ♪</font></i>

36:51.044 --> 36:52.856
<font color="#ff8080">[Monitor beeping]</font>

36:53.466 --> 36:55.133
<font color="#00ff00">Teddy:</font> Abby, hi.

36:56.469 --> 36:58.510
We were able to repair
your diaphragm.

36:58.596 --> 37:00.916
We had to place in a chest tube
for drainage,

37:01.002 --> 37:03.142
but that'll probably come out
in a few days.

37:03.803 --> 37:07.655
And your kit will stay here,
if you decide to report it.

37:08.213 --> 37:09.463
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

37:09.548 --> 37:11.399
You think I should do it, don't you?

37:11.484 --> 37:13.736
That is not
our call to make.

37:15.270 --> 37:18.018
But we do think that
you should talk to someone.

37:18.494 --> 37:20.204
Doesn't have to be your husband.

37:21.093 --> 37:22.537
But someone.

37:23.288 --> 37:25.724
I keep going over it
in my head.

37:27.234 --> 37:30.195
If I hadn't been
so distracted by my phone.

37:31.404 --> 37:33.087
If I had just trusted my gut

37:33.172 --> 37:35.867
and not gone down that street
with the broken lamplights.

37:35.952 --> 37:37.330
Abby.

37:38.707 --> 37:42.277
This was not your fault.

37:43.089 --> 37:44.957
You didn't ask
for this.

37:46.160 --> 37:49.651
There is nothing
you did to deserve this.

37:49.755 --> 37:51.434
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

37:52.191 --> 37:53.354
I can't.

37:53.440 --> 37:54.590
I just can't...

37:54.676 --> 37:56.410
Okay, that's okay.

37:57.596 --> 37:59.383
I'll check in on you
in a little bit, all right?

37:59.468 --> 38:00.623
Try to get some rest.

38:00.708 --> 38:01.716
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

38:01.801 --> 38:03.238
<font color="#00ff00">Woman on P.A.:</font>
<i>Dr. Felix to the ER.</i>

38:03.323 --> 38:04.666
<i>Dr. Felix to the ER.</i>

38:04.957 --> 38:07.817
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

38:09.147 --> 38:10.680
Jack...

38:13.963 --> 38:17.198
He's gonna look at me
and see this broken person.

38:17.383 --> 38:19.442
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

38:19.763 --> 38:23.807
If I tell him this,
it's all he'll ever see.

38:23.893 --> 38:25.193
Abby, look at me.

38:26.624 --> 38:28.474
This doesn't define you.

38:28.660 --> 38:31.111
And whether you tell
your husband or you report it

38:31.197 --> 38:34.067
or you don't tell another soul,
you're a survivor.

38:34.188 --> 38:35.940
You survived.

38:36.856 --> 38:39.229
I still feel nauseous
when I see

38:39.315 --> 38:42.089
men in expensive shoes
with the points of the toes,

38:42.174 --> 38:44.573
because that's how my ex-husband
made my kidney bleed.

38:44.690 --> 38:47.295
For years, I thought
I got what I deserved,

38:47.380 --> 38:49.932
that I was responsible,
that maybe,

38:50.032 --> 38:54.619
just maybe if I had said or done
one thing differently...

38:54.805 --> 38:56.403
But none of that was
your fault.

38:56.682 --> 38:57.965
No.

38:58.224 --> 39:01.059
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

39:03.090 --> 39:04.799
It's not your fault.

39:05.024 --> 39:07.098
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

39:07.286 --> 39:10.895
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes sharply]</font>

39:11.268 --> 39:13.335
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

39:13.780 --> 39:14.973
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

39:17.406 --> 39:19.753
Do you have a phone
I can use?

39:20.197 --> 39:21.381
Yes.

39:22.081 --> 39:24.849
<font color="#ff8080">[Beeping continues]</font>

39:26.716 --> 39:28.471
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes sharply]</font> Will you stay?

39:28.557 --> 39:30.518
As long as you need.

39:32.391 --> 39:35.557
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

39:35.967 --> 39:39.246
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

39:39.332 --> 39:41.284
<font color="#ff8080">[Breathes deeply]</font>

39:41.370 --> 39:42.753
<font color="#ff8080">[Sniffles]</font>

39:42.902 --> 39:45.252
<font color="#ff8080">[Cellphone buttons clicking]</font>

39:45.380 --> 39:46.954
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Slow down ♪</font></i>

39:47.039 --> 39:48.110
<font color="#ffff00">[♪♪]</font>

39:48.196 --> 39:51.610
<font color="#ff8080">[Line Ringing]</font>
- <i><font color="#ffff00"> ♪ Try to breathe in deep ♪</font></i>

39:51.696 --> 39:53.087
- <font color="#ff8080">[Siren wailing in distance]</font>
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Listen ♪</font></i>

39:53.172 --> 39:54.762
<font color="#ff8080">[Indistinct conversations]</font>

39:54.847 --> 39:55.763
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ To the words I speak ♪</font></i>

39:55.848 --> 39:58.094
Any game we watch on TV...
right? they...

39:58.180 --> 40:03.063
they run, toss, wrestle, chase,
until someone gets hurt.

40:03.222 --> 40:06.563
Or until someone calls "time out."

40:07.003 --> 40:08.453
Then the game stops.

40:08.594 --> 40:10.678
And no matter how much fun
they're having,

40:10.763 --> 40:12.657
everything stops.

40:12.743 --> 40:16.618
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Calling out for help, out for help ♪</font></i>
- That's consent.

40:16.868 --> 40:18.451
I thought
we were just having burgers.

40:18.641 --> 40:21.110
Yeah, well, I thought talking
was just talking,

40:21.196 --> 40:22.884
but you and I both know that's
not the same thing anymore,

40:22.969 --> 40:24.290
so...

40:25.227 --> 40:27.095
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Waiting to save yourself
from falling into deep ♪</font></i>

40:27.180 --> 40:30.131
You pay attention to the girl
you're with, all right?

40:30.216 --> 40:32.641
You... You... You need to care
about her feelings,

40:32.727 --> 40:33.493
her... her joy,

40:33.579 --> 40:35.411
at... at least as much
as you care about your own.

40:35.503 --> 40:36.651
- Okay, okay.
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't ♪</font></i>

40:36.745 --> 40:38.465
- And she gets to change her mind.
-<i><font color="#ffff00"> ♪ Let you down, my friend ♪</font></i>

40:38.551 --> 40:40.082
At any time.
I mean, if she says

40:40.168 --> 40:42.142
"stop," or
if she stops having fun, you...

40:42.228 --> 40:44.699
- you just plain stop.
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't let you fight alone ♪</font></i>

40:44.785 --> 40:45.926
Time out.

40:46.086 --> 40:47.887
- Game over.
- I know.

40:47.973 --> 40:51.496
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't leave you in the cold ♪</font></i>

40:51.582 --> 40:54.054
- Being with someone you like is...
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ On your own ♪</font></i>

40:54.139 --> 40:55.322
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't let you down, my friend ♪</font></i>

40:55.407 --> 40:58.277
There's nothing like it, and I
want you to be safe and happy,

40:58.363 --> 41:01.543
but that only happens
if she is, too.

41:01.941 --> 41:03.190
Okay.

41:03.315 --> 41:06.183
- Say it.
- <i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Come and sit with me down ♪</font></i>

41:06.276 --> 41:08.908
- Say it. <font color="#ff8080">[Slurps]</font>
<i><font color="#ffff00">- ♪ Pour out ♪</font></i>

41:09.307 --> 41:10.938
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Whatever's
weighing you down ♪</font></i>

41:11.023 --> 41:14.746
If she stops having fun,
just plain stop.

41:14.832 --> 41:16.301
Time out. Game over.

41:16.394 --> 41:17.855
Always.

41:18.479 --> 41:22.264
Now, pass those fries and tell
me what this Kelly is like.

41:22.350 --> 41:24.131
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Calm down, calm down ♪</font></i>

41:24.217 --> 41:25.382
Yeah.

41:26.338 --> 41:28.949
<i><font color="#00ff00">Meredith:</font> Too often,
trauma gets dismissed</i>

41:29.035 --> 41:30.762
<i>as "just in our head."</i>

41:31.343 --> 41:33.347
<i>- But the pain is real.
- <font color="#ffff00">♪ Waiting ♪</font></i>

41:33.433 --> 41:36.918
<i>- <font color="#ffff00">♪ To save yourself, save yourself ♪</font>
- We feel it...</i>

41:37.004 --> 41:40.215
<i>in our muscles, our cells,</i>

41:40.386 --> 41:43.404
<i>our hearts, our heads.</i>

41:43.489 --> 41:46.637
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ Stop running ♪</font></i>

41:46.723 --> 41:49.816
<i><font color="#ffff00">- ♪ Stop hiding ♪</font>
- And while there's no magic fix...</i>

41:50.082 --> 41:54.113
<i>- <font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't let you down, my friend ♪</font>
- ..no pill to make it disappear,</i>

41:55.063 --> 41:56.543
<i>we can ask for help.</i>

41:56.629 --> 42:00.054
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I won't let you fight alone ♪</font></i>

42:00.139 --> 42:03.043
Hey, I'm officially
no longer the interim chief,

42:03.129 --> 42:04.492
and officially starving.

42:04.577 --> 42:06.168
Can I take you out
to celebrate?

42:06.254 --> 42:07.535
I've had a rough day.

42:07.621 --> 42:09.191
I don't really feel like
celebrating.

42:09.277 --> 42:10.723
Yeah, well,
we can just talk.

42:10.823 --> 42:13.107
I just want to go home
and crawl into bed.

42:13.231 --> 42:14.543
All right, well,
we can do that.

42:14.676 --> 42:15.707
Alex, I'm tired.

42:15.808 --> 42:18.082
Can you just go celebrate
with Meredith?

42:18.168 --> 42:20.488
Jo, it's me.
You can talk to me.

42:20.583 --> 42:22.246
What... you think with
all my family crap

42:22.332 --> 42:23.611
that I'm gonna judge you?

42:23.697 --> 42:25.160
I'm not going to judge.

42:25.480 --> 42:28.668
Just, I just want
you talk to me.

42:28.763 --> 42:30.695
I don't want to talk
about it.

42:30.781 --> 42:32.425
Alex, I...

42:33.737 --> 42:35.365
I can't talk about it.

42:35.560 --> 42:37.159
I just want to go home.

42:37.626 --> 42:39.268
I want to go home alone.

42:39.498 --> 42:41.940
I want to go home
and sleep.

42:42.053 --> 42:43.714
Please.

42:47.037 --> 42:49.198
<i>It wont change tell
our truth.</i>

42:49.284 --> 42:51.705
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ You in the cold, on your own ♪</font></i>

42:51.791 --> 42:53.354
<i>Whenever we are ready.</i>

42:53.440 --> 42:57.073
<i><font color="#ffff00">♪ I wont
let you down my friend ♪</font></i>

